<font color="#00ffffff">Stories about you come up</font>
<font color="#00ffffff">the canal.</font>

00:17.390 --> 00:20.670
<font color="#00ffffff">Once you walked fine alone,</font>
<font color="#00ffffff">now you need a stick.</font>

00:20.710 --> 00:22.790
<font color="#ffffffff">You stay clean for two weeks,</font>

00:22.830 --> 00:24.470
<font color="#ffffffff">I'll write Linda another letter.</font>

00:24.510 --> 00:26.670
<font color="#ffff00ff">Have you recently suffered seizures?</font>

00:26.710 --> 00:29.510
<font color="#ffff00ff">It is Tuberculoma, I am</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">afraid it is inoperable.</font>

00:37.270 --> 00:41.510
<font color="#ffffffff">MUSIC: Lawman</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">by Girl Band</font>

01:52.230 --> 01:53.870
<font color="#ffff00ff">Mr Shelby.</font>

01:53.910 --> 01:56.270
<font color="#ffff00ff">I only gave opium to your brother</font>

01:56.310 --> 01:58.030
<font color="#ffff00ff">because he give me big trouble.</font>

01:58.070 --> 01:59.750
<font color="#ffff00ff">He attacked my wife.</font>

02:07.510 --> 02:10.389
<font color="#ffffffff">I would like a pot of green tea,</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">please.</font>

02:22.070 --> 02:24.310
<font color="#ffff00ff">It has taken me ten years</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">to build this business.</font>

02:24.350 --> 02:27.110
<font color="#ffffffff">Your business will be safe,</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">if you do what I say.</font>

02:30.910 --> 02:32.990
<font color="#ffffffff">How much opium do you have in</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">your cellar?</font>

02:34.550 --> 02:36.630
<font color="#ffff00ff">Five pounds.</font>

02:36.670 --> 02:38.070
<font color="#ffffffff">Bring it to me.</font>

02:39.670 --> 02:42.230
<font color="#ffffffff">Four minutes against the clock.</font>

03:14.070 --> 03:16.030
<font color="#ffffffff">As member of Parliament...</font>

03:18.550 --> 03:21.270
<font color="#ffffffff">..for this constituency...</font>

03:21.310 --> 03:23.790
<font color="#ffffffff">..it is my duty to take</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">responsibility for the welfare</font>

03:23.830 --> 03:26.390
<font color="#ffffffff">of my constituents.</font><font color="#ffff00ff"> Mr Shelby,</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">the clock is still ticking.</font>

03:26.430 --> 03:30.550
<font color="#ffffffff">The consumption of opium is very</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">prejudicial to health.</font>

03:30.590 --> 03:32.670
<font color="#ffffffff">Women give it to their children</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">so they can leave</font>

03:32.710 --> 03:35.190
<font color="#ffffffff">them untended while they work</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">in the factories.</font>

03:35.230 --> 03:37.830
<font color="#ffffffff">Men lose their jobs when they</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">become addicted.</font>

03:39.710 --> 03:42.310
<font color="#ffffffff">From now on, you will sell</font>

03:42.350 --> 03:45.950
<font color="#ffffffff">only cigarettes, cake and tea.</font>

03:47.230 --> 03:49.870
<font color="#ffffffff">If I hear that you are selling</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">opium again,</font>

03:49.910 --> 03:52.750
<font color="#ffffffff">time will indeed run out very</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">quickly for you. Do you understand?</font>

03:52.790 --> 03:55.390
<font color="#ffff00ff">Yes, I understand, I will stop.</font>

03:55.430 --> 03:57.430
<font color="#ffff00ff">Mr Shelby, the clock</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">is still ticking.</font>

04:04.230 --> 04:06.870
<font color="#ffffffff">Please tell...</font>

04:06.910 --> 04:10.470
<font color="#ffffffff">..your suppliers and your</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">customers...</font>

04:10.510 --> 04:12.670
<font color="#ffffffff">..that from now on...</font>

04:12.710 --> 04:15.830
<font color="#ffffffff">...there will be no more opium...</font>

04:15.870 --> 04:20.310
<font color="#ffffffff">..in Small Heath or in Bordesley.</font>

04:20.350 --> 04:22.029
<font color="#ffffffff">Thank you for the tea.</font>

04:49.870 --> 04:52.670
<font color="#ffffffff">BOMB EXPLODES</font>

05:00.070 --> 05:01.750
<font color="#ffffffff">You can let them through now.</font>

05:01.790 --> 05:03.550
<font color="#ffff00ff">Yes, sir, Mr Shelby.</font>

05:05.550 --> 05:09.070
<font color="#ffffffff">You tell the pub and cafe owners</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">in Montague Street...</font>

05:09.110 --> 05:11.190
<font color="#ffffffff">..if there is any further trade</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">in powder,</font>

05:11.230 --> 05:13.030
<font color="#ffffffff">there will be no more Montague</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">Street.</font>

05:13.070 --> 05:15.230
<font color="#ffffffff">I will have it demolished</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">and replaced by apartments.</font>

05:15.270 --> 05:18.030
<font color="#ffffffff">By order of Birmingham Urban</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">District Council.</font>

05:32.590 --> 05:35.310
<font color="#ffff00ff">Sorry I'm late, they closed Montague</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">Street.</font>

05:35.350 --> 05:37.710
<font color="#ffff00ff">There's a gas explosion or...</font>

05:42.550 --> 05:44.550
<font color="#ffff00ff">Right. Well, it would be nice if</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">just one thing</font>

05:44.590 --> 05:47.150
<font color="#ffff00ff">could happen in Birmingham that</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">wasn't our fault.</font>

05:51.830 --> 05:55.110
<font color="#ffffffff">I have gathered you all here today</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">because there is news</font>

05:55.150 --> 05:57.390
<font color="#ffffffff">and it is of interest to the whole</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">family.</font>

05:58.710 --> 06:00.470
<font color="#ffffffff">First of all,</font>

06:00.510 --> 06:03.670
<font color="#ffffffff">I would like to welcome Finn's new</font>

06:03.710 --> 06:06.030
<font color="#ffffffff">wife Mary to the family.</font>

06:07.710 --> 06:12.110
<font color="#ffff00ff">Right. Well, I'm very glad I dragged</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">myself out of bed for this.</font>

06:12.150 --> 06:13.910
<font color="#ffffffff">There is...</font>

06:13.950 --> 06:15.790
<font color="#ffffffff">..one more item of business.</font>

06:15.830 --> 06:16.910
<font color="#ffffffff">Johnny.</font>

06:16.950 --> 06:18.470
<font color="#00ffffff">Tom.</font>

06:19.710 --> 06:22.390
<font color="#00ffffff">Come on, come on, hurry up.</font>

06:29.030 --> 06:31.910
<font color="#ffffffff">Everyone...</font>

06:31.950 --> 06:35.070
<font color="#ffffffff">..this here is Erasmus.</font>

06:35.110 --> 06:37.390
<font color="#00ff00ff">Nobody calls me that.</font>

06:37.430 --> 06:40.390
<font color="#ffffffff">They call him Duke.</font>

06:41.830 --> 06:45.870
<font color="#ffffffff">20 years ago, at Appleby horse</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">fair...</font>

06:45.910 --> 06:47.270
<font color="#ffffffff">..I met a girl.</font>

06:47.310 --> 06:49.310
<font color="#ffffffff">We shared the shade of a hazel tree.</font>

06:50.390 --> 06:53.390
<font color="#ffffffff">Nine months later this lad was born.</font>

06:56.310 --> 06:58.510
<font color="#ffffffff">This is my son.</font>

06:58.550 --> 07:00.950
<font color="#ffffffff">His mother died on the road.</font>

07:00.990 --> 07:03.310
<font color="#ffffffff">Up until now I never tried</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">to find him.</font>

07:03.350 --> 07:07.390
<font color="#ffffffff">But I am trying to look at life in a</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">different way.</font>

07:09.430 --> 07:12.510
<font color="#ffffffff">A child is a precious thing.</font>

07:13.910 --> 07:15.270
<font color="#ffffffff">So I am bringing him...</font>

07:15.310 --> 07:17.670
<font color="#00ffffff">Into the fucking family with</font>
<font color="#00ffffff">a snap of his fingers.</font>

07:17.710 --> 07:20.950
<font color="#ffffffff">No, I am bringing him into the fold.</font>

07:20.990 --> 07:24.310
<font color="#ffffffff">He'll have to earn membership of</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">the family.</font>

07:24.350 --> 07:26.630
<font color="#ffffffff">For the moment, welcome, son.</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">You have a seat.</font>

07:26.670 --> 07:28.430
<font color="#ffffffff">Go on, sit down here.</font>

07:34.870 --> 07:37.470
<font color="#ffffffff">There are some mistakes I've made...</font>

07:37.510 --> 07:39.990
<font color="#ffffffff">..that I can never address...</font>

07:40.030 --> 07:41.350
<font color="#ffffffff">..and some I can.</font>

07:42.430 --> 07:44.230
<font color="#ffffffff">Some wounds I can try to heal.</font>

07:44.270 --> 07:46.470
<font color="#00ffffff">And new wounds you can open up.</font>

07:47.990 --> 07:49.190
<font color="#ffffffff">Anyway...</font>

07:50.390 --> 07:52.550
<font color="#ffffffff">..that's the business of the day.</font>

07:52.590 --> 07:54.590
<font color="#ffff00ff">Is it too early for whisky?</font>

08:01.670 --> 08:03.790
<font color="#00ffffff">There you go.</font>

08:03.830 --> 08:06.310
<font color="#00ffffff">Shelby breakfast for you, son.</font>

08:06.350 --> 08:08.390
<font color="#00ff00ff">I don't drink.</font>

08:08.430 --> 08:10.110
<font color="#00ff00ff">And I'm not a Shelby, all right?</font>

08:10.150 --> 08:12.510
<font color="#00ff00ff">I'm a Duke.</font>

08:12.550 --> 08:13.910
<font color="#ffffffff">Ooh, hoo, hoo, hoo.</font>

08:13.950 --> 08:15.430
<font color="#00ffffff">You're a fucking Shelby, all right,</font>

08:15.470 --> 08:17.630
<font color="#00ffffff">don't worry about that.</font>

08:17.670 --> 08:20.470
<font color="#00ffffff">Mm, I think we will need Curly</font>

08:20.510 --> 08:23.030
<font color="#00ffffff">and a strong rope to break this one</font>
<font color="#00ffffff">in, Tom.</font>

08:23.070 --> 08:25.150
<font color="#ffffffff">Arthur, open up the shop,</font>

08:25.190 --> 08:28.070
<font color="#ffffffff">put the kid here on the blackboard,</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">writing up the odds.</font>

08:28.110 --> 08:30.590
<font color="#00ff00ff">I can't write.</font>

08:30.630 --> 08:33.150
<font color="#ffffffff">Put the kid on the blackboard,</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">wiping off the chalk.</font>

08:36.150 --> 08:37.909
<font color="#ffffffff">Go on, son.</font>

08:37.950 --> 08:39.669
<font color="#00ffffff">Come on then.</font>

08:57.470 --> 09:00.510
<font color="#ffffffff">Lizzie, come on.</font>

09:06.870 --> 09:09.190
<font color="#00ff00ff">My father was the Duke of the Saxon</font>
<font color="#00ff00ff">Shore.</font>

09:09.230 --> 09:11.030
<font color="#00ff00ff">My mother was a Romany Queen.</font>

09:11.070 --> 09:13.710
<font color="#00ffffff">Who told you that, your mum?</font>

09:13.750 --> 09:16.310
<font color="#00ff00ff">I don't allow people to talk about</font>
<font color="#00ff00ff">my mother.</font>

09:18.750 --> 09:20.390
<font color="#00ffffff">Good for you.</font>

09:20.430 --> 09:23.110
<font color="#00ffffff">So let's get this right then,</font>
<font color="#00ffffff">you can't read,</font>

09:23.150 --> 09:25.510
<font color="#00ffffff">you can't fucking write,</font>
<font color="#00ffffff">there's nothing wrong with that.</font>

09:25.550 --> 09:27.950
<font color="#00ffffff">What can you do, eh?</font>

09:27.990 --> 09:29.830
<font color="#00ff00ff">I can tell the time.</font>

09:29.870 --> 09:31.230
<font color="#00ffffff">You can tell the time.</font>

09:31.270 --> 09:33.430
<font color="#00ffffff">Here, he can tell the time.</font>

09:33.470 --> 09:35.030
<font color="#00ffffff">Ain't that clever.</font>

09:36.310 --> 09:38.750
<font color="#00ff00ff">It's a lot more than you can</font>
<font color="#00ff00ff">fucking do.</font>

09:41.230 --> 09:43.430
<font color="#00ffffff">What did you just say to me?</font>

09:44.550 --> 09:46.590
<font color="#00ff00ff">What time is it, Mr Shelby?</font>

09:50.390 --> 09:52.070
<font color="#00ff00ff">That's what I can do.</font>

09:52.110 --> 09:55.110
<font color="#00ffffff">You little bastard.</font>

09:56.390 --> 09:58.630
<font color="#00ffffff">Here, keep it.</font>

09:58.670 --> 10:00.830
<font color="#00ffffff">Stop you from being late in</font>
<font color="#00ffffff">the future.</font>

10:28.550 --> 10:31.830
<font color="#ffffffff">Is there forgiveness in your heart</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">for Arthur Shelby?</font>

10:33.110 --> 10:34.630
<font color="#ffff00ff">No.</font>

10:37.830 --> 10:40.230
<font color="#ffff00ff">But maybe there will be forgiveness</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">from God.</font>

10:42.790 --> 10:45.230
<font color="#ffffffff">And you will do God's work?</font>

10:45.270 --> 10:48.110
<font color="#ffff00ff">God is interested in you as</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">well, Tommy.</font>

10:48.150 --> 10:52.190
<font color="#ffff00ff">And God will be with you on your</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">journey every step of the way.</font>

10:55.550 --> 10:57.750
<font color="#ffffffff">He may not need to take many steps.</font>

11:11.870 --> 11:13.270
<font color="#ffffffff">Tell me this, Linda...</font>

11:15.070 --> 11:18.350
<font color="#ffffffff">..is God interested in me...</font>

11:18.390 --> 11:20.110
<font color="#ffffffff">..or in my money?</font>

11:24.710 --> 11:26.750
<font color="#ffffffff">I believe you run a foundation</font>

11:26.790 --> 11:30.070
<font color="#ffffffff">and that your foundation has many</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">missions across the world</font>

11:30.110 --> 11:32.150
<font color="#ffffffff">but in these times of financial</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">crisis,</font>

11:32.190 --> 11:34.150
<font color="#ffffffff">funding is hard to come by.</font>

11:34.190 --> 11:37.990
<font color="#ffffffff">So perhaps your God's plan is</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">a practical one.</font>

11:38.030 --> 11:41.390
<font color="#ffffffff">Perhaps he would like me to make</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">a donation</font>

11:41.430 --> 11:43.350
<font color="#ffffffff">to your foundation</font>

11:43.390 --> 11:46.750
<font color="#ffffffff">and in return, he would like you</font>

11:46.790 --> 11:50.270
<font color="#ffffffff">to help my brother on his road</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">to redemption.</font>

11:50.310 --> 11:52.630
<font color="#ffffffff">Now, I know that in a place of</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">worship such as this,</font>

11:52.670 --> 11:54.870
<font color="#ffffffff">you would never ask how much.</font>

11:54.910 --> 11:57.430
<font color="#ffffffff">So I will tell you plainly.</font>

11:57.470 --> 12:00.790
<font color="#ffffffff">I will write your foundation</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">a cheque for £10,000...</font>

12:00.830 --> 12:03.150
<font color="#ffff00ff">Praise the Lord.</font>

12:03.190 --> 12:05.950
<font color="#ffffffff">..if you agree to look kindly on</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">Arthur and to help him.</font>

12:08.990 --> 12:13.750
<font color="#ffffffff">I need to look after everyone in</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">the family.</font>

12:13.790 --> 12:15.470
<font color="#ffffffff">Do we have a deal?</font>

12:18.430 --> 12:22.430
<font color="#ffff00ff">Your money will be spent to do good</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">around the world.</font>

12:22.470 --> 12:24.550
<font color="#ffff00ff">And a mission will be named</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">after you.</font>

12:27.830 --> 12:30.430
<font color="#ffff00ff">But I am only agreeing to help</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">him...</font>

12:30.470 --> 12:32.510
<font color="#ffff00ff">..not sleep with him.</font>

12:32.550 --> 12:34.790
<font color="#ffffffff">No.</font>

12:34.830 --> 12:37.670
<font color="#ffffffff">Now, I imagine the negotiation for</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">that particular favour</font>

12:37.710 --> 12:39.990
<font color="#ffffffff">would take a considerable amount of</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">time...</font>

12:41.510 --> 12:43.430
<font color="#ffffffff">..and I have an appointment.</font>

12:45.030 --> 12:46.790
<font color="#ffffffff">God bless.</font>

13:09.470 --> 13:12.190
<font color="#ffff00ff">Apologies for the initial</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">misunderstanding.</font>

13:13.830 --> 13:16.030
<font color="#ffffffff">My brother dealt with it.</font>

13:22.190 --> 13:24.190
<font color="#ffffffff">For the care you took.</font>

13:25.870 --> 13:28.630
<font color="#ffff00ff">Even though I succumbed</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">to temptation.</font>

13:28.670 --> 13:31.470
<font color="#ffffffff">Part of the reason my brother is</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">back dealing with it,</font>

13:31.510 --> 13:34.310
<font color="#ffffffff">is down to you, you spoke to him.</font>

13:34.350 --> 13:35.750
<font color="#ffff00ff">As a comrade.</font>

13:35.790 --> 13:37.590
<font color="#ffffffff">The beating is still owed to you.</font>

13:37.630 --> 13:39.150
<font color="#ffff00ff">Do you still do that kind of work</font>

13:39.190 --> 13:40.670
<font color="#ffff00ff">yourself, Thomas Shelby, MP?</font>

13:42.030 --> 13:45.750
<font color="#ffffffff">Mr Stagg, see, I can use men like</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">you.</font>

13:48.230 --> 13:51.110
<font color="#ffffffff">I have friends that are in need</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">of guns.</font>

13:52.630 --> 13:54.390
<font color="#ffffffff">Soon, there will be a shipment</font>

13:54.430 --> 13:59.150
<font color="#ffffffff">of Thompson sub machine guns</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">coming here from Boston.</font>

13:59.190 --> 14:02.190
<font color="#ffffffff">And I need you to unload</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">and store those weapons.</font>

14:04.070 --> 14:06.510
<font color="#ffffffff">There will also be ammunition...</font>

14:07.870 --> 14:09.070
<font color="#ffffffff">..like this.</font>

14:10.190 --> 14:12.550
<font color="#ffffffff">You have a good look.</font>

14:12.590 --> 14:16.670
<font color="#ffffffff">And I need you to take better care</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">of the guns and ammunition</font>

14:16.710 --> 14:18.310
<font color="#ffffffff">than you did of the powder.</font>

14:19.550 --> 14:20.590
<font color="#ffffffff">You understand?</font>

14:21.710 --> 14:23.670
<font color="#ffffffff">Previously,</font>

14:23.710 --> 14:28.390
<font color="#ffffffff">all of my import and export</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">went through Belfast docks.</font>

14:28.430 --> 14:30.070
<font color="#ffffffff">Now we're dealing with Boston...</font>

14:32.790 --> 14:36.790
<font color="#ffffffff">..I am considering shifting</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">my supply line to Liverpool.</font>

14:37.990 --> 14:39.430
<font color="#ffffffff">You'll be a very rich man.</font>

14:43.350 --> 14:45.350
<font color="#ffffffff">Don't you ever say thank you?</font>

15:03.230 --> 15:04.550
<font color="#ffff00ff">Thank you.</font>

15:09.590 --> 15:11.270
<font color="#ffff00ff">Is that why you do it, Mr Shelby?</font>

15:13.070 --> 15:15.350
<font color="#ffff00ff">Is that why you keep all this going?</font>

15:15.390 --> 15:17.430
<font color="#ffff00ff">To have people say thank you?</font>

15:18.950 --> 15:21.070
<font color="#ffff00ff">You could close all this down.</font>

15:21.110 --> 15:23.470
<font color="#ffff00ff">You could leave the sport behind.</font>

15:23.510 --> 15:26.910
<font color="#ffff00ff">You could live like</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">an ordinary mortal man.</font>

15:26.950 --> 15:29.350
<font color="#ffff00ff">On your gravestone -</font>

15:29.390 --> 15:30.950
<font color="#ffff00ff">"an ordinary mortal man".</font>

15:32.790 --> 15:34.390
<font color="#ffff00ff">But, instead,</font>

15:34.430 --> 15:37.910
<font color="#ffff00ff">you still go round collecting</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">"please" and "thank you"</font>

15:37.950 --> 15:41.070
<font color="#ffff00ff">and "sorry"</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">and "forgive me, Mr Shelby."</font>

15:42.950 --> 15:44.310
<font color="#ffff00ff">Is that what it's all for?</font>

15:47.150 --> 15:48.230
<font color="#ffffffff">You want to know?</font>

15:49.630 --> 15:51.310
<font color="#ffffffff">You want to know</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">why I've carried on...</font>

15:52.870 --> 15:54.470
<font color="#ffffffff">..all these years?</font>

15:55.910 --> 15:57.270
<font color="#ffffffff">It's so I can do this.</font>

16:02.110 --> 16:03.790
<font color="#ffffffff">And then...</font>

16:04.870 --> 16:06.230
<font color="#ffffffff">..do this.</font>

16:10.710 --> 16:12.110
<font color="#ffffffff">Feel it?</font>

16:13.950 --> 16:15.230
<font color="#ffff00ff">I feel it.</font>

16:17.830 --> 16:19.510
<font color="#ffffffff">Junk doesn't even come close.</font>

16:23.910 --> 16:25.270
<font color="#ffffffff">Soon, Mr Stagg...</font>

16:26.990 --> 16:29.270
<font color="#ffffffff">..when my last piece</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">of business is done...</font>

16:31.910 --> 16:33.110
<font color="#ffffffff">..I will indeed...</font>

16:34.670 --> 16:36.230
<font color="#ffffffff">..be an ordinary mortal man.</font>

16:39.510 --> 16:40.670
<font color="#ffffffff">You have a good day.</font>

16:47.750 --> 16:51.270
<font color="#00ffffff">Arthur,</font>
<font color="#00ffffff">we've got a problem with a referee.</font>

16:51.310 --> 16:52.790
<font color="#00ffffff">He's not taking the money.</font>

16:52.830 --> 16:54.510
<font color="#00ffffff">He's fucking religious</font>
<font color="#00ffffff">or something.</font>

16:54.550 --> 16:56.270
<font color="#ffff00ff">Jesus Christ.</font>

16:58.910 --> 17:01.510
<font color="#00ffffff">With Tommy away, you're in charge</font>
<font color="#00ffffff">of gambling, Arthur,</font>

17:01.550 --> 17:03.550
<font color="#00ffffff">what shall we do?</font>

