<font color="#ffff00ff">better than all of them.</font>

50:19.350 --> 50:20.910
<font color="#ffff00ff">Blood here is like wine,</font>

50:20.950 --> 50:24.110
<font color="#ffff00ff">like the vintage wine</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">in that bottle. It's the label,</font>

50:24.150 --> 50:27.110
<font color="#ffff00ff">it's the terroir,</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">it's the grape that makes the wine.</font>

50:27.150 --> 50:29.750
<font color="#ffff00ff">Who fucking cares</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">about the glass around it?</font>

50:29.790 --> 50:32.310
<font color="#ffff00ff">And you, my friend,</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">you're an American.</font>

50:32.350 --> 50:34.590
<font color="#ffff00ff">You fucking smash the glass,</font>

50:34.630 --> 50:36.030
<font color="#ffff00ff">you spill the blood</font>

50:36.070 --> 50:38.190
<font color="#ffff00ff">and you spend their currency</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">to get what you want.</font>

50:39.750 --> 50:40.910
<font color="#ffff00ff">Am I right?</font>

50:43.190 --> 50:45.630
<font color="#ffff00ff">When you come to America,</font>

50:45.670 --> 50:47.830
<font color="#ffff00ff">I will show you things.</font>

50:47.870 --> 50:49.190
<font color="#00ffffff">You're going to America?</font>

50:51.670 --> 50:55.270
<font color="#ffffffff">To Canada, Lizzie,</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">to collect payment for the shipment.</font>

50:55.310 --> 50:56.550
<font color="#ffffffff">I need to do it myself.</font>

50:58.230 --> 51:00.110
<font color="#00ffffff">And who will be going with you?</font>

51:00.150 --> 51:02.710
<font color="#ffff00ff">Michael will be there</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">to watch his back.</font>

51:02.750 --> 51:05.630
<font color="#00ffffff">Another journey, Tommy?</font>

51:05.670 --> 51:07.310
<font color="#ffff00ff">$5 million, Mrs Shelby.</font>

51:07.350 --> 51:09.390
<font color="#ffff00ff">It's worth a little cruise,</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">don't you think?</font>

51:13.350 --> 51:16.870
<font color="#ffffffff">You know whiskey does talk,</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">Mr Nelson,</font>

51:16.910 --> 51:20.230
<font color="#ffffffff">and sometimes</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">whiskey is...very eloquent.</font>

51:22.390 --> 51:26.310
<font color="#ffffffff">But $5 million, Mr Nelson...</font>

51:28.270 --> 51:29.590
<font color="#ffffffff">Now, that is a legacy.</font>

51:31.550 --> 51:35.310
<font color="#ffffffff">And when I come back,</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">I will know everything.</font>

51:37.790 --> 51:42.790
<font color="#ffff00ff">I see myself so clearly</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">in you, Thomas Shelby.</font>

51:44.350 --> 51:47.470
<font color="#ffff00ff">You are a man with a bright</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">and glittering future.</font>

51:47.510 --> 51:49.030
<font color="#ffffffff">DOOR OPENS</font>

51:50.950 --> 51:53.590
<font color="#00ffffff">Mr Shelby,</font>
<font color="#00ffffff">there's a car coming up the drive.</font>

51:53.630 --> 51:55.150
<font color="#00ffffff">A Rolls-Royce.</font>

51:55.190 --> 51:56.670
<font color="#00ffffff">Were you expecting more guests?</font>

51:58.710 --> 51:59.910
<font color="#ffffffff">No.</font>

52:06.790 --> 52:08.270
<font color="#ffffffff">Excuse me.</font>

52:16.550 --> 52:18.870
<font color="#00ff00ff">We were on our way</font>
<font color="#00ff00ff">to my constituency in Smethwick</font>

52:18.910 --> 52:21.310
<font color="#00ff00ff">and I heard our American friend</font>
<font color="#00ff00ff">was in Birmingham</font>

52:21.350 --> 52:23.110
<font color="#00ff00ff">and that he was coming here,</font>

52:23.150 --> 52:26.790
<font color="#00ff00ff">so we came</font>
<font color="#00ff00ff">to say one last farewell.</font>

52:29.870 --> 52:32.470
<font color="#00ff00ff">Champagne.</font>
<font color="#00ff00ff">We have much to celebrate.</font>

52:40.750 --> 52:42.990
<font color="#00ff00ff">It isn't that I wasn't sure</font>
<font color="#00ff00ff">Mr Shelby would give you</font>

52:43.030 --> 52:45.830
<font color="#00ff00ff">an excellent send-off,</font>
<font color="#00ff00ff">I just felt,</font>

52:45.870 --> 52:48.430
<font color="#00ff00ff">since telegrams and wires</font>

52:48.470 --> 52:51.910
<font color="#00ff00ff">and letters can so easily</font>
<font color="#00ff00ff">be intercepted,</font>

52:51.950 --> 52:54.670
<font color="#00ff00ff">we might confirm all that</font>
<font color="#00ff00ff">we've achieved during your visit</font>

52:54.710 --> 52:56.190
<font color="#00ff00ff">over champagne.</font>

52:57.310 --> 53:00.870
<font color="#ffff00ff">It is remarkable how quickly</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">our relationships have developed.</font>

53:00.910 --> 53:03.550
<font color="#ffff00ff">So many triangles in this room.</font>

53:03.590 --> 53:06.910
<font color="#ffff00ff">Everyone except from Mr Nelson</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">is the point of a triangle.</font>

53:08.470 --> 53:10.510
<font color="#00ffffff">How am I part of a triangle?</font>

53:10.550 --> 53:14.670
<font color="#00ff00ff">Mr Nelson,</font>
<font color="#00ff00ff">you have all that you came for?</font>

53:14.710 --> 53:17.030
<font color="#ffff00ff">I have confirmation</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">that the future of Europe is in</font>

53:17.070 --> 53:19.670
<font color="#ffff00ff">the hands of men like yourselves.</font>

53:19.710 --> 53:23.910
<font color="#00ff00ff">And that urgent conversations</font>
<font color="#00ff00ff">between Washington,</font>

53:23.950 --> 53:26.830
<font color="#00ff00ff">Rome and of course Berlin</font>
<font color="#00ff00ff">can now begin.</font>

53:28.350 --> 53:31.150
<font color="#00ff00ff">A two-week visit that may have</font>
<font color="#00ff00ff">changed the course of history.</font>

53:32.590 --> 53:34.110
<font color="#ffff00ff">We have all got what we wanted.</font>

53:34.150 --> 53:35.710
<font color="#ffff00ff">Yes.</font>

53:35.750 --> 53:39.430
<font color="#ffff00ff">And I got what I have wanted</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">from the moment I set eyes on it.</font>

53:44.670 --> 53:47.990
<font color="#ffff00ff">Elizabeth,</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">you are a very lucky woman...</font>

53:49.110 --> 53:52.790
<font color="#ffff00ff">..to have each day</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">what I have only sampled once.</font>

54:15.910 --> 54:17.310
<font color="#00ff00ff">Forgive us, Mr Nelson,</font>

54:17.350 --> 54:19.110
<font color="#00ff00ff">that was a necessary bit</font>
<font color="#00ff00ff">of housekeeping.</font>

54:24.870 --> 54:25.950
<font color="#00ff00ff">Thomas.</font>

54:27.830 --> 54:29.750
<font color="#00ff00ff">We do so hate to be indiscreet,</font>

54:29.790 --> 54:33.030
<font color="#00ff00ff">but we have told you many times,</font>

54:33.070 --> 54:37.910
<font color="#00ff00ff">if you are to seek power</font>
<font color="#00ff00ff">in these days of shiny magazines</font>

54:37.950 --> 54:40.390
<font color="#00ff00ff">and society photographs,</font>

54:40.430 --> 54:42.350
<font color="#00ff00ff">sooner or later,</font>
<font color="#00ff00ff">you will have to find a spouse</font>

54:42.390 --> 54:43.470
<font color="#00ff00ff">who is more suitable.</font>

54:45.150 --> 54:47.070
<font color="#00ff00ff">A woman with Lizzie's past</font>

54:47.110 --> 54:49.550
<font color="#00ff00ff">and personal history</font>
<font color="#00ff00ff">really isn't suitable.</font>

54:52.230 --> 54:54.190
<font color="#00ff00ff">She doesn't deserve you, Mr Shelby.</font>

55:18.350 --> 55:20.190
<font color="#ffffffff">You know the thing is, Mosley...</font>

55:21.590 --> 55:22.630
<font color="#ffffffff">..you're right.</font>

55:26.030 --> 55:27.630
<font color="#ffffffff">You're right,</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">she doesn't deserve me.</font>

55:32.630 --> 55:34.110
<font color="#ffffffff">She doesn't deserve what I am.</font>

55:36.750 --> 55:39.350
<font color="#ffffffff">She doesn't deserve</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">what I will become.</font>

55:39.390 --> 55:42.030
<font color="#ffff00ff">What will you become?</font>

55:42.070 --> 55:44.950
<font color="#ffffffff">The truth is, I belong here,</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">at this table.</font>

55:44.990 --> 55:46.670
<font color="#ffffffff">With fuckers like you.</font>

55:48.870 --> 55:50.310
<font color="#ffffffff">She doesn't.</font>

55:53.510 --> 55:55.750
<font color="#ffffffff">For all I try to hide it...</font>

55:57.190 --> 55:59.310
<font color="#ffffffff">HE SCOFFS</font>
<font color="#ffffffff">..I'm just one of you.</font>

56:04.310 --> 56:06.630
<font color="#ffffffff">Could there be a sadder ending, eh?</font>

