57:10.390 --> 57:12.950
<font color="#ffff00ff">Mr Nelson's prepared</font>
<font color="#ffff00ff">to get you out of here.</font>

57:14.070 --> 57:16.670
<font color="#ffff00ff">But first he needs an answer</font>
