<font color="#ffff00ff">If the answer is no...</font>

57:27.390 --> 57:28.630
<font color="#ffff00ff">..you'll stay.</font>

57:31.910 --> 57:33.430
<font color="#ffffffff">I have consulted my mother.</font>

